commit.title: Make whitespace linter not check for trailing newlines.
commit.message:
Make whitespace linter not check for trailing newlines.

git does not know how to fix this automatically when they appear by
removing a chunk of text at the end of the file.

eg
```
foo

bar
```
to
```
foo

```
